# Discography

This page is my **living catalog**—the official index of Hash Blink releases inside the Hash Blink Universe. I update it as releases finalize, editions lock, and links go public.

**Primary public source used to populate this list (auto-updating):**
- Shazam “Releases” index for Hash Blink (Apple ecosystem feed).  [oai_citation:0‡Shazam](https://www.shazam.com/artist/hash-blink/1468831319/releases)  
**Artist hub (Apple Music):**
- Apple Music artist page.  [oai_citation:1‡Apple Music - Web Player](https://music.apple.com/us/artist/hash-blink/1468831319)  

> **Note:** Shazam’s Releases page is a great “master feed,” but it may not show *everything* (some regional/older items can be missing). If anything is missing, I’ll sync it once you confirm it’s on Apple Music.

---

## How the catalog is organized

### Types
- **Album** — full-length release
- **EP** — shorter body of work
- **Single** — standalone release

### Status tags
- **Released** — live on platforms
- **In Vault** — archived, not public yet
- **Scheduled** — date/window set
- **Revision** — updated/remastered/versioned

### Vault fields I track for each entry
- Release date (or target window)
- Edition(s) (Standard / Deluxe / Vault / Archive)
- Credits (if available)
- Cover/art status (Final / Draft / Pending)
- Public links (Apple Music / etc.)

---

## Core series and pillars (canon)
- **Pipeline Prophecies** — origin-coded series rooted in Monrovia environments  
- **The Blood Scripture** — darker conceptual body of work  
- **The Oracle Tapes** — prophetic narrative series  
- **History Ain’t What They Told Us** — concept-driven historical line  
- **Ash Broadcast / Ticker Bones / Rationed Static** — 1925–1934 broadcast arc  
- **Grave Pact** — Scroll/arc releases and editions

